{"tid":16864,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"M記自助點餐機之我見","createTime":"2016-12-01T15:22:38.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T19:54:09.000Z","uid":2739,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"62f0b564ad15e164a5584dee43f586ae076eac06","tid":16864,"uid":2739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T15:22:38.000Z","msg":"平時我去M記食一般都會叫8號餐，咁一般來講唔使十五秒就點好，下面有例子：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 職員<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：8號餐加大可樂少冰喺度食。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：多謝你27蚊<br />\n八達通機 ：嘟！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早幾日我去咗旺角M記，原來裝修過，加咗幾部點餐機喺度。我唔係想打擊呢D idea，但係真係唔好用囉！<br />\n<br />\n首先係個分類，我想叫麥樂雞，但係我係套餐分類見唔到雞嘅物體，原來雞個分類用咗麥香雞包(定係脆辣雞腿包）做圖示。字又細丶圖又大，一時之間我撚睇到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！<br />\n<br />\n仲有就係我習慣可樂叫少冰，我摸咗差唔多10秒先知原來係下面個行㩒更改個制個度改，嘩第一次用真係估你撚度咩！<br />\n<br />\n今日又去咗食，諗住挑戰下自己可以幾快點到餐，結果係58秒，啫係平時嘅大約4x，仲要唔係個個人都咁快，平均應該分半鐘左右。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係話你idea唔好，但係真係唔方便囉！"},{"pid":"03f3429dd49a8ff6cd6950ee8fc4b7c7600d45f5","tid":16864,"uid":32765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T15:23:29.000Z","msg":"第一城m記？"},{"pid":"2c9c4c10bc22b339a4ee1fa97115ca54643547b3","tid":16864,"uid":2739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T15:32:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一城m記？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n旺角"},{"pid":"db28416e6f9d395aaedabf04633d8ad6cc4be23c","tid":16864,"uid":12980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T16:05:50.000Z","msg":"樓豬on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b13a781addaee1fcfdb210447069d9f95a432afd","tid":16864,"uid":26176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T16:11:22.000Z","msg":"你係咪有點餐障礙？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.