faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：可樂<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：係度食定拎走？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：係度食<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：係多謝你23蚊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：加大呀屌你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最後都係冇少冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講慢D囉⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n8號餐 加大 飲可樂少冰 喺度食。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n加唔加個蘋果批？"},{"pid":"d0720d98e7fb283b96cefe428deb4f3a882d5a51","tid":16864,"uid":22889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T17:33:33.000Z","msg":"部機設計我就冇乜意見既<br />\n係啲用家唔識用又要霸住嚟用先最on9<br />\n嘩屌你有次兩部機一個啊嬋一個中坑<br />\n喺到又加又減又加又減啲野食<br />\n燥到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e1f83274137372988f8e22e8a186b4c7c9ae4e5","tid":16864,"uid":9544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T17:38:34.000Z","msg":"我想問 脆辣雞腿飽多醬 個多醬 有冇得咁？"},{"pid":"719ae957aacdd5ef482b6757c6528b22923c9c4a","tid":16864,"uid":88,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T17:41:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想問 脆辣雞腿飽多醬 個多醬 有冇得咁？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有 但你要落包個陣 就要去揀<br />\n過左再揀 要刪左 再禁過<br />\n<br />\n利申 用過一次 唔會再用<br />\n慢撚到位街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54fe3d6872e7b8fd406adc461ad3ffad8088a8c1","tid":16864,"uid":25278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T17:42:03.000Z","msg":"好似無走鹽同走冰既制"},{"pid":"391e4b8f89bbe124be98b44a0d63d4edee20a467","tid":16864,"uid":12019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T17:42:32.000Z","msg":"部機感應得幾慢就真<br />\nbtw 點都方便過排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88446a367146e61a6a7845987bb143b2b1f30c5e","tid":16864,"uid":12731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c